snippet.title: Ultimate Chicken Horse: Elephantastic Update and PS4 Launch Date
snippet.description:
Ultimate Chicken Horse launches on PS4 on December 12th with the new Elephantastic Update (available for PC on the same day)! Try out the new Challenge mode, where you can build, share and compete globally for best times on user-created levels. A new character, new blocks, new levels and more!

Want to know when other consoles launch? 
- Sign up for our newsletter: https://www.cleverendeavourgames.com/signup
- Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/ClevEndeavGames
- Join the official Discord: http://www.discord.gg/uch

Want more details about the update? See our blog post at http://cleverendeavourgames.com/consoleupdate
